												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/elizabethcostello/">Elizabeth Costello</a></h6>
													Elizabeth Costello has lived in Turkey, Spain, Mexico, France, and in several American cities. Her previous publications include the poetry chapbook <em>RELIC</em> and her collaborators include dancers, poets, and musicians. <em>The Good War</em> is her first novel. She lives in Portland, Oregon.																									</div>
